										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>歐元兌日圓匯率在暴跌之前出現了又一輪飆升，暗示日本央行可能會介入。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-32683 aligncenter" src="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/EURJPY-–-4H-Chart.png" alt="EURJPY – 4H Chart" width="832" height="633" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/EURJPY-–-4H-Chart.png 832w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/EURJPY-–-4H-Chart-300x228.png 300w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/EURJPY-–-4H-Chart-768x584.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 832px) 100vw, 832px" /></p>
