										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>歐元兌日圓本週將聚焦GDP成長數據，有進一步下行的可能。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-26874 aligncenter" src="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EURJPY-–-Daily-Chart.png" alt="EURJPY – Daily Chart" width="720" height="637" srcset="https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EURJPY-–-Daily-Chart.png 720w, https://www.atfx.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/EURJPY-–-Daily-Chart-300x265.png 300w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></p>
